-- Australia Reduces Resource Tax to 30% to Win Agreement From Large Miners
-- Tim Smith
-- 2010-07-01T22:01:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/australia-reduces-resource-tax-to-30-to-win-agreement-from-large-miners.html

          
          
             Australia will charge a 30 percent
mineral resource rent tax as part of its agreement with
industry, according to a press release from Prime Minister Julia
Gillard today.  
